---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | SATL Lab">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">About</h1>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
      <p style="color: var(--satl-text-dim);">
        전자공학과 3학년. 회로, 신호, 반도체, 전파를 공부하고
        재현 가능한 형태로 정리합니다.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold" style="color: var(--satl-text);">
        Tech Stack
      </h2>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {["Python", "C++", "Arduino", "LTspice", "MATLAB", "Git"].map((t) => (
          <span class="satl-chip">{t}</span>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold" style="color: var(--satl-text);">
        Contact
      </h2>

      <p style="color: var(--satl-text-dim);">
        GitHub:
        <a
          href="https://github.com/"
          target="_blank"
          class="hover:underline"
          style="color: var(--satl-text);"
        >
          github.com/your-id
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>